snippet.title: Monster Showdown - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam!!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/616680/Monster_Showdown/

Monster Showdown is an action packed VR shooter. Survive an onslaught of increasingly strong Monsters. Explore your environment to find new weapons and upgrades to strengthen yourself. Take down the horde and escape the nightmare!
